- When migrating from the old architecture to the new one, always remember:
    - If necessary, split services into repositories, freezed models and providers
    - All ATProto endpoints are in `@lib/lexicons/`, create models if needed
    - For storage, get a storage manager from the get it
    - For cache, get a cache manager interface from the get it
    - For logging, use the logging framework
    - For auth, get a AuthRepository from the get it
    - For API calls, check if `@lib/src/core/network/sprk_repository_interface.dart` already has that method in its contract
        - If it does, get it from the get it
    - Don't forget to add repositories to the service locator at `@lib/src/core/di/service_locator.dart`
    - DO NOT import ANYTHING from the old architecture